{
  "chapter": 6,
  "chapter_summary": "小蝶在水边再次出现，质问欲投河自尽的孟星魂是否真正活过，触动其内心。孟星魂回到快活林，发现高老大已变得冷酷无情。高老大得知小何擅自去找孙玉伯执行刺杀任务，既愤怒又无奈。孟星魂想去查看小何的生死，高老大以任务为重为由断然拒绝，甚至说出不能为死人牺牲活人的话。此时十二飞鹏帮坛主屠城邀请高老大赴宴，高老大敏锐地意识到孙玉伯与万鹏王的争执正是刺杀老伯的最佳时机，赶去打探消息。本章深刻揭示了高老大冷酷的生存哲学和孟星魂内心的矛盾挣扎。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "你想死？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "你想死，我并不劝你，我只问你一句话。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "我只问你，你活过没有？",
      "tone": "深沉",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiao_die",
      "speaker_name": "小蝶",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "一个人若连活都没有活过，就想死，岂非太愚蠢了些？",
      "tone": "怜悯",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "你回来了？",
      "tone": "平淡",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑惑",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "小何呢？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "小何？谁知道他疯到哪里去了，这一阵他没事做。",
      "tone": "随意",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "咱们都一样，没事做的时候，就找不着人了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "我见过他。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "你见过他？在哪里？",
      "tone": "急切",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "他去找过我。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "他为什么去找你？",
      "tone": "动容",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "你知道他到哪里去了？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "等等走……我问你，他是不是想替你去找孙玉伯呢？",
      "tone": "急切",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "你就让他去了？",
      "tone": "质问",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "他已经去了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "你明知道孙玉伯是个怎么样的人，你去最多也不过只有六七成把握，他去简直是送死，你为什么让他去？",
      "tone": "怒斥",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "他怎么知道我住在那里的？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "我不是怪你，只不过是为他担心而已，你们无论谁有了危险，我都同样担心。",
      "tone": "缓和",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "你想到哪里去？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "去该去的地方！",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "现在你已经不能去了。",
      "tone": "断然",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "不能去？",
      "tone": "疑惑",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "小何若已去找过孙玉伯，不论他是死是活，孙玉伯必然已经有了警觉，你再去就太危险了。",
      "tone": "理性",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "我去的地方，哪次不危险？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "但这次却不同。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "没有什么不同，只要是我该做的事，我就要做好它。",
      "tone": "坚定",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "就算你要去，也得等到这件事情冷下来再说。",
      "tone": "沉吟",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "那时小何也已冷了。",
      "tone": "悲凉",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "现在他也已经冷了。",
      "tone": "叹息",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "我至少应该去瞧瞧。",
      "tone": "坚持",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "不行，你不能冒险，我不能为了任何人让你去冒险。",
      "tone": "断然",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "连他也不行？",
      "tone": "追问",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "他也不行，更不行，我不能为了一个死人将活人牺牲。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "但他是我们的兄弟。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "兄弟是一回事，任务是一回事，我们若不能将这两样事分开，明天死的就是我们！",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "我们若死了，连收尸的人都没有。",
      "tone": "冷酷",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "什么事？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_men_wai_ren",
      "speaker_name": "门外人",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "屠二爷想请你去喝酒。",
      "tone": "恭敬",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_men_wai_ren",
      "text": "屠城？",
      "tone": "确认",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_men_wai_ren",
      "speaker_name": "门外人",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "是。",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好，我知道了，我就去。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "你知不知道屠城是什么人？",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "屠城表面虽是个大商人，其实却是‘十二飞鹏帮’的坛主，也是万鹏王手下的第一号打手。",
      "tone": "沉思",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "他就是屠大鹏？",
      "tone": "确认",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "他就是。",
      "tone": "肯定",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "你知不知道最近孙玉伯曾经派律香川去找过万鹏王？",
      "tone": "反问",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "speaker_name": "孟星魂",
      "listener": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "text": "我知道律香川走了，却不知道他去找谁，也没有打听。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "律香川是孙玉伯最看重的人，若不是为了重要的事，他绝不会轻易派他出去。",
      "tone": "分析",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "孙玉伯和万鹏王有了争执，我们的事就有希望，屠城这次离开大鹏坛，说不定就是冲着孙玉伯来的。",
      "tone": "兴奋",
      "chapter": 6
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_gao_lao_da",
      "speaker_name": "高老大",
      "listener": "char_meng_xing_hun",
      "text": "我们再去打听打听，你最好在这里等着。",
      "tone": "急切",
      "chapter": 6
    }
  ],
